        <num>44-9-22</num>
        <content>
          <p>Any easement obtained for the purpose of ensuring the exposure of a solar energy device shall be created in writing and shall be subject to the same requirements of conveyance and recording as other easements.</p>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1978, p. 2076, ยง 3.)</p>
